        </p>

        <p>The HRMS App includes:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Employee Self-Service (ESS)</li>
            <li>Attendance: Clock-in & Clock-out</li>
            <li>Leave requests</li>
            <li>Employee profile & documents</li>
            <li>Payroll information (optional)</li>
            <li>Notification & messaging features</li>
        </ul>

        <p>The App is intended for employees of companies using the Greater Change HRMS platform.</p>
