    <section class="section">
        <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>

        <h3>2.1 Personal Information</h3>
        <p>We may collect:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Employee name</li>
            <li>Email address</li>
            <li>Phone number</li>
            <li>Employee ID</li>
            <li>Designation & department</li>
            <li>Profile photo (optional)</li>
            <li>Company details</li>
            <li>Login credentials (securely encrypted)</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>2.2 Attendance & Geo-Location Data</h3>
        <p>To support Clock-In / Clock-Out, we may collect:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Device location (GPS)</li>
            <li>IP address</li>
            <li>Time of clock-in and clock-out</li>
            <li>Geo-coordinates for attendance verification</li>
        </ul>
        <p>‚úî Location is collected only during attendance actions and not in the background.</p>

        <h3>2.3 Device Information</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Device type</li>
            <li>Operating system</li>
            <li>App version</li>
            <li>Crash logs & performance data</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>2.4 Usage Data</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Pages viewed</li>
            <li>Buttons clicked</li>
            <li>Session duration</li>
            <li>Feature usage analytics</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
        <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use collected information for:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Employee authentication & account access</li>
            <li>Marking attendance & verifying work location</li>
            <li>Providing ESS functions</li>
            <li>Processing leave requests</li>
            <li>HR & payroll calculations</li>
            <li>App improvement & performance monitoring</li>
            <li>Sending HR-related notifications</li>
        </ul>

        <p>We do <strong>not</strong> use your data for:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Advertising</li>
            <li>Selling to third parties</li>
            <li>Marketing without permission</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
        <h2>4. Location Permission (Required by Apple & Google)</h2>
        <p>The App requires location access ONLY during Clock-In/Clock-Out to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Verify employee attendance</li>
            <li>Prevent false or remote check-ins</li>
            <li>Maintain accurate HR records</li>
        </ul>
        <p>‚úî The App does NOT track location continuously.</p>
        <p>‚úî Location is collected only when you manually tap Clock-In or Clock-Out.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
        <h2>5. Data Sharing</h2>
        <p>We may share information only with:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Your employer using the HRMS system</li>
            <li>Prabha Technologies (developer) for technical support</li>
            <li>Secure cloud hosting providers</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We NEVER sell or trade personal information.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
        <h2>6. Data Storage & Security</h2>
        <p>We use industry-standard security practices:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Encrypted databases</li>
            <li>SSL/TLS communication</li>
            <li>Role-based authorization</li>
            <li>Firewalls & multi-layer protection</li>
            <li>Regular vulnerability checks</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Prabha Technologies manages backend infrastructure.<br>
        Greater Change controls access to employee records.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
        <h2>7. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>Your data is retained until:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Your employment remains active</li>
            <li>Your employer maintains an account with Greater Change</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
            On deletion request, personal data is securely removed while attendance logs may remain archived per labor laws.
            You may request deletion through your HR department.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
        <h2>8. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You may request:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Access to your data</li>
            <li>Correction of inaccurate details</li>
            <li>Deletion of optional data</li>
            <li>Restriction of certain processing</li>
            <li>Withdrawal of optional permissions</li>
        </ul>
